snippet.title: Spell Card Collection - Extra Spell Cards (No Commentary)
snippet.description:
𝘛𝘩𝘦 𝘧𝘪𝘯𝘢𝘭 𝘣𝘰𝘴𝘴 𝘩𝘢𝘴 𝘥𝘦𝘴𝘤𝘦𝘯𝘥𝘦𝘥.

So... yeah... let's not beat around the bush. This here's the final eight cards in the game that stand above and beyond everything else in the game. Be it spells that require special understanding, finding that one trick, or just plain getting good, you need to prepare yourself for one hell of a gauntlet ahead.

Music

Extra Spell BGM - New Star Nova by 島白
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DHDlUydnKcE

Ultamate Spell BGM - The Final Battle ~Unwavering Thoughts in my Heart~ by Wingless Seraph
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=NDEPtX4_-kk

Spell Cards

0:12 - "Trick Number"
1:47 - "Time Leap"
2:45 - "Great Seven-Colored Bunraku"
3:45 - "The Twelve Divine Generals of the Heavenly World of Salvation"
6:04 - "Angelic Elements"
7:58 - "Lost Phantasm"
9:37 - "Paradox of Phenomenal Judgment"
13:51 - "Exteinnzion"

Translation's courtesy of the Touhou wiki

Click here to vote on the next game for me to play
https://goo.gl/VrhGV1

You can download the script here
http://www.bulletforge.org/u/shijimi_nono/p/spellcardcollection
